      <h1>Eternos, Your Life Archive</h1>
       
      <p>
        Here’s how it works - simply link your social media accounts to Eternos one time and in minutes, you’re already backing up your online material, life milestones, and treasured memories for future generations. If you're not into social networking you can upload video, important documents, and photos via our direct file upload. Eternos displays your activity in an easy-to-understand timeline where all of your activity is tracked and permanently saved. Here’s an example - let’s say you post something to your Facebook wall; within seconds it will then automatically show up in your Eternos timeline and is immediately stored and archived, giving you the ability to go back and locate, view, and recall exactly what and when you posted. Easy as 1-2-3! 
      </p>		
    </div>
